      <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
         <head>Biographical History</head>
         
      <p>John Pierotti (1911-1987) was an American cartoonist and illustrator. Pierotti worked for several organizations during his career, most extensively for King Features Syndicate and <emph render="italic">The New York Post</emph>.</p></bioghist>
      
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
         <p>The <emph render="bold">John Pierotti Papers</emph> consists of original editorial cartoons, sports cartoons, magazine and advertising illustrations, original sketches, magazine and newspaper clippings of Pierotti's work, photographs, correspondence and published material.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      
